<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[60582]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Marx's "Das Kapital" comes to the Grec]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[The young director Sylvain Creuzevault offers a stage-adaptation of Karl Marx's most famous work, as part of the Grec Festival.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Boasting such shows as <i>Le père tralalère</i> and <i>Notre terreur</i>, the French performance company D’ores et déjà and the young director Sylvain Creuzevault caught the attention of France&#8217;s world of theatre.</p>
<p>They are now staging the secret structures of the capitalist world our lives are organised around, as you can read in <i>Das Kapital</i>, a tough-going work that Marx left unfinished.</p>
